### Clean Separation (ARCHITECTURAL BOUNDARIES)
```
- Website (this repo): Pre-launch landing page, static content, waitlist collection
- Mobile App (separate repo): Actual RideCareShare application development
- No duplication: Website is purely informational, app handles all functionality
```

