## DEPLOYMENT & OPERATIONS

### GitHub Pages Deployment
**Automatic deployment process:**
```bash
# 1. Ensure main branch is up to date
git status
git add .
git commit -m "descriptive message"
git push origin main

# 2. GitHub Pages automatically deploys from main branch
# 3. Site available at: https://vadimgumarov.github.io/ridecareshare_web/

# 4. Custom domain setup (after DNS configuration):
# - ridecareshare.com (primary)
# - ridesharetogether.com (redirect to primary)
```

### Service URLs & Endpoints
```
Development:
- Local: file:///Users/vadim/Desktop/Projects/RIDECARESHARE_WEB/index.html
- Local server (optional): http://localhost:8000

Production:
- GitHub Pages: https://vadimgumarov.github.io/ridecareshare_web/
- Custom Domain (primary): https://ridecareshare.com
- Custom Domain (secondary): https://ridesharetogether.com
```

