## TESTING STRATEGY (MANUAL)

### Browser Testing
```
Required browsers:
- Chrome (latest)
- Firefox (latest)
- Safari (latest, macOS/iOS)
- Edge (latest)

Test checklist:
1. All sections render correctly
2. Theme toggle works (light/dark mode)
3. Smooth scroll navigation functions
4. Waitlist form captures data
5. Social media links open in new tabs
6. Responsive design works (mobile, tablet, desktop)
7. No JavaScript console errors
8. Fast page load (< 2 seconds)
```

### Accessibility Testing
```
- Use Chrome Lighthouse for accessibility audit
- Test keyboard navigation (Tab, Enter, Space)
- Test screen reader compatibility (VoiceOver on macOS)
- Verify sufficient color contrast in both themes
- Ensure all images have alt text (when added)
- Verify ARIA labels on interactive elements
```

### Performance Testing
```
- Lighthouse performance score > 90
- First Contentful Paint < 1.5s
- Largest Contentful Paint < 2.5s
- Cumulative Layout Shift < 0.1
- No render-blocking resources
```

