## SECURITY & COMPLIANCE

### Security Requirements
```
- No authentication needed (static site)
- No sensitive data stored (waitlist emails sent to service)
- HTTPS enforced via GitHub Pages
- Content Security Policy via meta tags (if needed)
- No third-party scripts (privacy-friendly)
```

### Privacy & Data Collection
```
- Waitlist form: Name and email only
- No tracking scripts or analytics (unless explicitly added)
- No cookies (except localStorage for theme preference)
- Privacy-first approach
```

